<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">About This Project</h1>
            
            <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title h3 mb-3">Room Booking System</h2>
                    <p class="lead">
                        A comprehensive web application designed to streamline the process of booking and managing rooms 
                        for various purposes including meetings, conferences, workshops, and study sessions.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-3">Project Purpose</h3>
                    <p>
                        This system was developed to solve the common problem of double-booking and scheduling conflicts 
                        in shared spaces. It provides a centralized platform where users can:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>View available rooms with detailed information</li>
                        <li>Book rooms for specific time periods</li>
                        <li>Manage existing bookings</li>
                        <li>Avoid scheduling conflicts with automatic detection</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-3">Technology Stack</h3>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h5>Backend</h5>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>ASP.NET Core 8.0 MVC</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Entity Framework Core 9.0</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>SQL Server LocalDB</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>C# 12.0</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h5>Frontend</h5>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Bootstrap 5</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Bootstrap Icons</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>jQuery</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Responsive Design</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

