                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <h5><i class="bi bi-building text-primary me-2"></i>Room Management</h5>
                                <p>Full CRUD operations for managing rooms including creation, editing, viewing details, and deletion.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <h5><i class="bi bi-calendar-check text-success me-2"></i>Booking System</h5>
                                <p>Create, view, and cancel bookings with automatic conflict detection to prevent double-booking.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <h5><i class="bi bi-shield-check text-info me-2"></i>Data Validation</h5>
                                <p>Comprehensive form validation ensuring data integrity and user-friendly error messages.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <h5><i class="bi bi-phone text-warning me-2"></i>Responsive UI</h5>
                                <p>Mobile-friendly interface that works seamlessly across all device sizes.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
